flowchart TD
    Start[Unscheduled Pod] --> Queue[Pop Pod from Queue]
    Queue --> LoopNodes[Iterate over all nodes in cluster]
    
    subgraph Predicate Filtering
        direction TB
        Taint[Node Taints & Tolerations matched?]
        Fit[NodeResourcesFit: CPU/Mem/Storage available?]
        Ports[NodePorts: Port conflicts?]
        Affinity[NodeAffinity / selector matches?]
        Volume[VolumeZone / Topology limits?]
    end
    
    LoopNodes --> Taint
    Taint -->|Yes| Fit
    Taint -->|No| RejectNode[Reject Node & record fail reason]
    
    Fit -->|Yes| Ports
    Fit -->|No| RejectNode
    
    Ports -->|Yes| Affinity
    Ports -->|No| RejectNode
    
    Affinity -->|Yes| Volume
    Affinity -->|No| RejectNode
    
    Volume -->|Yes| AcceptNode[Keep Node in feasible list]
    Volume -->|No| RejectNode

    RejectNode --> CheckNext{All nodes evaluated?}
    AcceptNode --> CheckNext
    
    CheckNext -->|No| LoopNodes
    CheckNext -->|Yes| Final[Output Feasible Nodes List]

    style RejectNode fill:#f43f5e,stroke:#be123c,color:#fff
    style AcceptNode fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
